{
  "stem": "16930.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 304.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I guess they had to pay off their mortgage and other expenses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And by renting out a room, one room, and-- because this boy-- other boy and I shared one room-- by feeding them, they got a little money in.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was like a part-time job for the lady of the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, she was-- she was at home anyway, so she took two more meals, you know, the same time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that's how they make their ends meet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were eating in like-- it was like a-- in the kitchen, like a dining-- side-- like a dining-- side dining place in the-- in the kitchen or next to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this lady was busy all the time, salting the meat and-- and putting-- and-- and washing it-- you know, like she a real-- almost like a rebbetzin, you know?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then one day, my roommate told me that he was walking up the street and following her-- saw she went in a non-Jewish butcher shop.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he looked through the window and saw her buying meat there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said, I can't believe it, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There she was, doing all these things and, like, you know, washing and everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She must've washed several times and salted several times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] don't believe me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Just ask her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I asked her, and she said yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I don't know how she rationalized it, because in that-- in those days, you had-- everything was rationed with coupons.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That-- that fellow gave her extra meat off the ration book, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's why she shopped there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I guess the price was cheaper for non-kosher food and for meat than for kosher meat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So she justified it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
